    "description": "Expeditors India Advisory Limited invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Distribution Manager at our Jaipur location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Expeditors India Advisory Limited:\nExpeditors India Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jaipur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Expeditors India Advisory Limited!",
